DiSiCal
=======

    DiSiCal (Distributed Simple Calendar) is a CORBA/Java application for 
    managing the appointments of a small to medium-sized user group via a 
    web based interface.  DiSiCal is intended to be used as an example project 
    in courses on distributed computing.

