Project tree overview
---------------------

	Project source root:                       ./src/de/cwrose/disical
	Configuration/Property-files:              ./etc
	Scripts (Db creation, helpers)             ./bin
    Project library jar files:                 ./lib
    Project distribution jar files:            ./dist
    User documentation:                        ./doc
    Project specification documents (German):  ./spec	
	IDL's/Castor XML-files:                    In source tree
	Compiled classes:                          In source tree/excluded from cvs


